<p>E há também uma função de busca posicionada de forma intuitiva para maior conveniência.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="495" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-1024x495.png" alt="17 Search" class="wp-image-115208" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-1024x495.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-768x371.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-1536x742.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-600x290.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-760x367.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-1440x696.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-740x358.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1-385x186.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="495" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-1024x495.png" alt="18 Looking for" class="wp-image-115212" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-1024x495.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-768x372.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-1536x743.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-600x290.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-760x368.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-1440x697.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-740x358.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1-385x186.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Menos trabalho para os visitantes significa que eles podem encontrar os produtos que querem sem nenhuma complicação e isso aumenta a probabilidade de realizarem uma compra.&nbsp;</p>



<h2>12. Ter avaliações e classificações de produto é o segundo elemento mais importante (Statista)</h2>



<p>As compras online são divertidas e emocionantes, mas também podem ser frustrantes às vezes.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Os compradores geralmente precisam comparar diversos produtos para encontrarem o que estão procurando, e todas as opções os deixam levemente paralisados.</p>



<p>Uma das melhores formas de aumentar a confiança do cliente para que tenham a clareza de que precisam é oferecendo-lhes acesso às avaliações e classificações dos produtos.&nbsp;</p>



<p>De fato, este é o atributo mais importante para a experiência de compra online para <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/973413/most-important-attributes-online-shopping-shoppers-usa/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">53 por cento</a> das pessoas. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="697" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-1024x697.png" alt="19 Top percent" class="wp-image-115215" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-1024x697.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-300x204.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-768x523.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-1536x1046.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-380x259.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-600x409.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-760x518.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-1440x981.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-73x50.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-720x490.png 720w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-220x150.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1-385x262.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1.png 1636w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Você poderia até afirmar que ter estas informações prontamente disponíveis formam uma grande parte do sucesso da Amazon.</p>



<p>Afinal de contas, ela facilita bastante para que você encontre a classificação dos produtos que vendem, além de avaliações detalhadas dos clientes.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="499" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-1024x499.png" alt="20 customer review" class="wp-image-115217" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-1024x499.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-1536x748.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-600x292.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-760x370.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-1440x702.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-740x361.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1-385x188.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px