<h2 id="13">13. Ter custos extras é o motivo principal pelo abandono de carrinho (Baymard Institute)</h2>



<p>Uma alta <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/cart-abandonment-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">taxa de abandono de carrinho</a> em compras pode ser facilmente um dos maiores obstáculos para criar uma loja de comércio eletrônico bem-sucedida.</p>



<p>Por isso, é extremamente importante que você saiba como manter isso em cheque e os motivos específicos pelos quais os compradores falham em concretizar suas compras.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Embora existam diversos motivos para o abandono de carrinho durante a finalização de uma compra, custos extras como frete, impostos e tarifas são os principais.</p>



<p>De fato, metade de todos os compradores abandonam o carrinho durante o processo de finalização de compra por causa disso. (<a href="https://baymard.com/lists/cart-abandonment-rate" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Fonte</a>.)</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="724" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-1024x724.png" alt="24 Top statistics" class="wp-image-115229" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-1024x724.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-300x212.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-768x543.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-1536x1085.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-380x268.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-600x424.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-760x537.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-1440x1017.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-71x50.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-693x490.png 693w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-220x155.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1-385x272.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1.png 1888w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Por isso é importante ser transparente quanto a estes custos e oferecer frete grátis quando possível.&nbsp;</p>



<p>A marca de roupas modernas <a href="https://www.mycentsofstyle.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Cents of Style</a>, por exemplo, sempre oferece frete grátis e permite que os compradores saibam disso assim que chegam em seu site.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="501" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-1024x501.png" alt="25 Scents of Style" class="wp-image-115236" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-1024x501.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-300x147.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-768x376.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-1536x751.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-380x186.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-600x294.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-760x372.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-1440x705.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-102x50.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-740x362.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1-385x188.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><em>“Nossos fretes são sempre gratuitos.”</em></p>



<h2 id="14">14. Forçar o comprador a criar uma conta é o segundo motivo principal pelo abandono de carrinho (Baymard Institute)</h2>



<p>Pesquisas revelaram que <a href="https://baymard.com/lists/cart-abandonment-rate" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">28 por cento</a> dos compradores falharam ao concretizar uma compra porque foram obrigados a criar uma conta. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="729" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-1024x729.png" alt="26 Abandonment reasons" class="wp-image-115238" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-1024x729.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-300x214.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-768x547.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-1536x1093.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-380x270.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-600x427.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-760x541.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-1440x1025.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-688x490.png 688w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-220x157.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1-385x274.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1.png 1894w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Eu sei que eu pessoalmente acho irritante quando eu faço minhas compras online, adiciono itens no meu carrinho e estou pronto para efetuar o pagamento. Mas de repente, eu me deparo com a temida tela de “crie uma conta para prosseguir.”</p>



<p>Embora não seja um problema tão grave se eu planejo fazer uma compra com uma empresa, várias e várias vezes, é um grande incômodo se eu quiser fazer apenas uma compra única. E aparentemente, várias outras pessoas compartilham o mesmo sentimento. É por isso que eu sugiro dar aos compradores a opção de realizar a compra como convidado.</p>



<p>Isso reduz muito do atrito e permite que os compradores efetuem a compra de seus objetos sem muita frustração e sem ter que passar pelo processo de criar uma conta.</p>



<p>É isso o que faz a marca de móveis e decoração do lar, <a href="https://www.crateandbarrel.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Crate and Barrel</a>, e isso funciona excelentemente. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="345" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-2.png" alt="27 Crate &amp; Barrel" class="wp-image-115243" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-2.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-2-300x173.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-2-380x219.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-2-61x35.png 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-2-87x50.png 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-2-220x127.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-2-385x221.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></figure></div>



<h2 id="15">15. O retargeting dos visitantes do site faz com que tenham uma probabilidade 43 por cento maior de realizarem uma compra (PR Newswire)</h2>



<p>Infelizmente, não importa o quanto a sua loja de comércio eletrônico seja incrível, <a href="https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/study-92-percent-of-consumers-visiting-a-retailers-website-for-the-first-time-arent-there-to-buy-300390086.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">92 por cento</a> dos compradores não irão comprar nada logo de cara. </p>



<p>Eles podem simplesmente estar fazendo a pesquisa inicial, “olhando as vitrines” virtuais ou simplesmente não estarem com intenção de compra ainda.</p>



<p>A questão é que maior parte deles não irão gerar uma venda logo na primeira vez em que chegarem ao seu site.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Mas isso não quer dizer que eles escaparam dos seus dedos e estão perdidos para sempre.</p>



<p>Fazer o retargeting dos visitantes provou ser altamente eficaz para manter as marcas de comércio eletrônica na mira dos clientes e gentilmente guiá-los de volta aos produtos nos quais estiveram interessados.</p>



<p>Por exemplo, a Hawthorne, uma empresa que vende produtos de cuidados pessoais para homens, usa este anúncio de retargeting no Facebook para chamar a atenção dos visitantes passados e direcioná-los de volta ao seu site.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="814" height="1024" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-814x1024.png" alt="28 Hawthorne" class="wp-image-115245" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-814x1024.png 814w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-238x300.png 238w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-768x967.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-380x478.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-600x755.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-760x957.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-28x35.png 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-40x50.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-389x490.png 389w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-220x277.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1-385x485.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-1.png 1044w" sizes="(max-width: 814px) 100vw, 814px" /></figure></div>



<p>“O retargeting lhes dá um pequeno empurrão para a sua marca,” diz o estrategista de conteúdo <a href="https://blog.spiralytics.com/retargeting-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Pierre de Braux</a>.</p>



<p>“Quando um cliente em potencial vê um anúncio de retargeting, há uma probabilidade de 70 por cento de que ele irá realizar a compra do seu produto em vez do produto do seu competidor.”</p>



<p>Portanto, esta é absolutamente uma tática que deve ser considerada em 2020 e durante os anos próximos.&nbsp;</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5ea160a34171b" class="block-content-upgrade">
