										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>17 das melhores propostas de valor para comércio eletrônico que conhecemos</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-1024x437.jpg" alt="E-Commerce Value Propositions [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-115122" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1-385x164.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/E-Commerce-Value-Propositions-Wordpress-1.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5fcf8bcec0668" class="block-preamble"><p>A competição no comércio eletrônico é feroz. E está prestes a ficar ainda mais intensa.</p>
</div>






<p>Com <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/439576/online-shopper-conversion-rate-worldwide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">2,42% das visitas de comércio eletrônico</a> se convertendo em compras, os marqueteiros estão procurando constantemente por novas formas de persuadir seus visitantes e de se destacarem entre seus competidores.</p>



<p>Com inúmeras opções para escolher, os clientes pensam no que diferencia sua marca de comércio eletrônico.</p>



<p>A resposta está escondida em sua <em>proposta de valor.</em></p>



<p>Sua proposta de valor é a primeira coisa que você quer que seus clientes em potencial conheçam.</p>



<p>Com uma proposta de valor atraente, você pode convencer os seus clientes em potencial a tomarem uma ação e continuarem seu caminho no seu <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-sales-funnel" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">funil de vendas de comércio eletrônico</a>.</p>



<p>Mas vamos ao mais importante primeiro.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5ea160a34171b" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
